  <h1>Welcome to CometJet!</h1>
  <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>

  <p>We are happy to inform you that you have been accepted as a pilot in CometJet. Congratulations! We are sure that we are leaving one of our aircraft in good hands.</p>

  <p>Your application and passion for aviation made a great impression on us. Your enthusiasm fits perfectly with our mission to provide the highest quality aviation services to our passengers.</p>

  <hr />

  <p>To fully join CometJet crew, you must join our airline on the <a href="#">Newsky platform</a>. It allows you to organize, track and save all your flights.</p>

  <p>Before your first flight, please read the SOP (Standard Operating Procedures) and download the livery for your aircraft, which you can find by clicking <a href="#">HERE</a>.</p>

  <p><strong>Need training?</strong> Don’t worry! You can sign up for our official training <a href="#">HERE</a>.</p>

  <hr />

  <p><strong>FOR MSFS PLAYERS:</strong><br />We recommend downloading the MSFS add-on for Katowice–Pyrzowice Airport EPKT. It’s our HUB, so this will help a lot. Download it <a href="#">HERE</a>.</p>

  <hr />

  <p>Join our Discord to access all information and ask questions anytime!</p>

  <p class="footer">KayJaykay and Airaced – CometJet VA CEOs</p>

